h2. Common Examples.

It&#39;s not possible to give every possible example because date formatting can be complex, and it varies from region to region.  Here are a few common examples that demonstrate how to use the output filters below.

||Example Output||The Filter Parameters||
|Thu Apr 14, 2011|{{\[\[\*createdon:strtotime:date=`%a %b %e, %Y`\]\]}}|
|18 April 2011|{{\[\[\*createdon:strtotime:date=`%e %A %Y`\]\]}}|
|Monday, April 18, 2011|{{\[\[\*createdon:strtotime:date=`%A, %B %e, %Y`\]\]}}|
|2011-04-18|{{\[\[\*createdon:strtotime:date=`%Y-%m-%d`\]\]}}|

