|%n|Newline character|\n| 
|%p|am or pm|amz|
|%P|AM or PM|AM| 
|%r|Same as %I:%M:%S %p|08:23:11 PM|
|%R|Same as %H:%M|23:11|
|%S|Second|00 to 59|
